=== Usage ===
Use the odd parameters for atoms (automatically linked) or miscellaneous text, and the even parameters for number of atoms. For example:
* <tt><nowiki>{{Chemical formula|H|2|O}}</nowiki></tt> produces: {{Chemical formula|H|2|O}}
* <tt><nowiki>{{Chemical formula|H2O}}</nowiki></tt> produces: {{Chemical formula|H2O}}
* <tt><nowiki>{{Chemical formula|H|2|S||O|4}}</nowiki></tt> produces: {{Chemical formula|H|2|S||O|4}}
* <tt><nowiki>{{Chemical formula|H|2|SO4}}</nowiki></tt> produces: {{Chemical formula|H|2|SO4}}

